Installation Instructions
*************************

The build system is moved to meson and simplified. To configure the project
and build the project do below:
	mkdir build && cd build
	meson ..
	meson install
	
There are two possible optional values that can be defined:
	-Dinstall-schemas to install GSettings schema
	-Dinstall-gconf   to install deprecated GConf schemas

To see details fun meson configure
